# Add known subdomains to monitor directly (one per line).
# These FQDNs will be added to the database and probed for liveness and
# change detection on every scan cycle, without running full enumeration.
#
# Useful for: third-party assets, partner domains, or subdomains you already
# know about and want to track without rediscovery overhead.
#
# Lines starting with # are treated as comments and ignored.
#
# Example entries:
admin.example.com
api.example.com
staging.example.com
dev.example.com
vpn.example.com
mail.example.com
